            <h1 class="main-title">
                <div class="md-title"><span itemprop="headline">How a Piece of Malaysian Flight 370 Drifted 2,300 Miles</span></div>
            </h1>
        
        
            <div class="article__deck"><p>Indian Ocean debris moves in predictable patterns and confirms searchers are looking in the right spot for the missing plane.</p>
</div>
        
    
    


